    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/998ac2d90b520df09276cefaafd12dbd.poster.avif?t=1765099475\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/998ac2d90b520df09276cefaafd12dbd.webm?t=1765099475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/998ac2d90b520df09276cefaafd12dbd.mp4?t=1765099475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paper Wars 是一款单人飞行动作游戏，您可以驾驶强大的纸飞机。对抗一群红色纸飞机，以及陆地和海上威胁。解锁并升级您的舰队以称霸天空！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备精良的纸飞机</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些纸飞机可不是普通的！它们配备了枪械、导弹等武器。根据你的风格自定义飞机，选择不同的武器和装备。用你升级后的纸飞机，在空中、陆地和海洋中与敌人展开对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/14ccac6169fc3ec58fa05a5c357a1b4e.poster.avif?t=1765099475\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/14ccac6169fc3ec58fa05a5c357a1b4e.webm?t=1765099475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280650/extras/14ccac6169fc3ec58fa05a5c357a1b4e.mp4?t=1765099475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
